reviewText: Please, please, please make this available.  I had it on VHS and need it on DVD.  It's awesome.  Even the music is great!
This is the greatest baseball highlight video of all time, at least for 1995ish and before.

For the price, this was a much better compilation of Baseball's great moments and bloopers than I expected. I got it for my son because it was cheap and I figured I couldn't go wrong. I ended up really enjoying it. There were quite a few things I hadn't seen before. If you like baseball you can't go wrong.
